General Information

Autili Zinc with Vitamin Cchewable tablets contain zinc and vitamin C. it maintains general health and well being. Zinc helps regulate healthy appetite and support healthy immune system function. Vitamin C helps promote the absorption of iron and modulate the immune system.

Warnings

Keep out of reach of children.This product is taken as an assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. Do not take with similar zinc and vitamin c products in case of exceeding recommended daily dose.

Directions

Tablets should be chewed carefully.Children should consume under adults supervision. 1-10 yrolds, take 1 tablet daily; above 11 yrs. and adults, take 1-2 tablets daily; or directed by your healthcare professional.
